Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.33,0:00:22.58,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Polly Jean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.83,0:00:25.54,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}We'll never be away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.54,0:00:27.13,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}We're going
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.46,0:00:31.63,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}We're always here in between
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.59,0:00:40.06,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}The shadows and the trees, in between
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.14,0:00:44.06,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Like sunshine trickling through the leaves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.10,0:00:48.02,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}I want to feel something real
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.06,0:00:51.61,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Like rivers overflowing
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.86,0:00:55.82,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}I want to be set free
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.82,0:00:59.49,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Now everything is part of me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.62,0:01:03.62,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}A world to reach, nothing to fear
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.62,0:01:07.17,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}I don't know where they're going
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.42,0:01:11.17,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Now won't you come find me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.21,0:01:15.13,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Though I try, and I try, and I try, and I try
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.13,0:01:18.68,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Can never shake off this feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.93,0:01:22.97,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Don't know why, don't know why, don't know why, don't know why
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.02,0:01:26.73,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Why we hide from you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.81,0:01:28.15,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Polly Jean
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.19,0:01:31.90,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}We'll never be away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.90,0:01:33.40,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}We're going
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.78,0:01:38.03,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}We're always here in between
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.91,0:01:41.66,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Those shadows everywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.70,0:01:43.29,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Seventeen
